description: A dashboard for visualizing results from the k6.io load testing tool, using the InfluxDB exporter for the k6 test API https://test-api.loadimpact.com/

targets.query: SELECT mean("value") FROM "checks" WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY "check", "group"
